{"tid":2128214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[好慘好慘] 方艙醫院即是木馬","createTime":"2020-07-27T22:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T23:55:47.000Z","uid":12929,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"27db37f1e35090f1f9647d6a468fd3a6c19cd967","tid":2128214,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T22:44:38.000Z","msg":"兩篇嘢要連埋黎睇就會知港共想做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>亞博館隔離中心以避免播毒為由 強制院友使用尿片</ins><br />\n//此外，該名院友亦曾向職員查詢可否洗澡，他引述職員指14日均不會獲安排洗澡，而他入住亞博後已3日，至今天才有職員為他抹身。院友形容做法並不人道，批評職員不允許檢疫人士去廁所，又不安排他們洗澡，令衞生情況差劣。//<br />\n1. <a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200727/bkn-20200727190635525-0727_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200727%2Fbkn-20200727190635525-0727_00822_001.html&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=1dfcd5fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200727/bkn-20200727190635525-0727_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>方艙醫院即是木馬</ins><br />\n//在這個背景下設立「方艙」，提供極需要的隔離床位予輕症病人，表面上，符合邏輯。但如以上所講，為送至亞博的病人貼上「不用醫」的標籤，就給了港共上下其手的機會。<br />\n<br />\n不難想像，港共輿論會將亞博病人，寫成是香港醫生的「棄兒」。<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">好慘好慘</span></span>，所以呢？就派大陸醫生來救援！<br />\n<br />\n這個做法有幾個好處：一）突顯香港醫護貪財、怕病毒，放棄香港人；二）反襯黨醫的英勇，在高風險下拯救香港人，即使醫死人都「雖敗猶榮」； 三）避免雙方醫護在公立醫院裏針鋒相對（或literally 拎針筒互隊）。//<br />\n2. <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/方艙醫院即是木馬/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%96%B9%E8%89%99%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E5%8D%B3%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%A8%E9%A6%AC%2F&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=a2a98437\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%96%B9%E8%89%99%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E5%8D%B3%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%A8%E9%A6%AC%2F&h=2e18daef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/方艙醫院即是木馬/</a>"},{"pid":"df61feb313f4d7713ee9b06f9da9a8a2ca9836f9","tid":2128214,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T23:13:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b771969ba81165d130831afc4e61fe123f61f97","tid":2128214,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T23:15:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c8ceba24719ad87b0cf49ba76b637be6a9922a0","tid":2128214,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T23:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cec354c93dc663ba8a746eb51bb565e64dcc36f","tid":2128214,"uid":63300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T23:28:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b48b395f875a7b0cf8b86bb5d2af3344a090267c","tid":2128214,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T23:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91035ad74bdeb0c3ea558b6d0c236720caa5cd28","tid":2128214,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T23:55:47.000Z","msg":"推"}]}